OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy this morning with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain spreading
OL,7,Fnortheastwards. Rain slowly easing
OL,8,Fthis afternoon and skies eventually
OL,9,Fbrightening, but scattered slow moving
OL,10,Fshowers also building. These could be
OL,11,Fheavy and possibly thundery towards
OL,12,Fthe evening.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers continuing on and off
OL,15,Fthis evening, largely easing as skies
OL,16,Fclear during the second half of the
OL,17,Fnight. Locally gusty winds developing,
OL,18,Fparticularly across and close to
OL,19,Fhigher ground.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
