OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FVariable amounts of cloud but
OL,6,Fa dry, fairly bright and breezy day
OL,7,Ffor many. Some intermittent rain
OL,8,Fpossible at times, mainly across
OL,9,Fwestern hills, though this fairly
OL,10,Fisolated. Feeling warmer.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloud
OL,13,Fand rain giving way to sunshine and
OL,14,Fshowers on Monday. Temperatures
OL,15,Ftrending lower. Rather cool and breezy
OL,16,FTuesday and Wednesday with sunny
OL,17,Fspells, scattered showers and possible
OL,18,Fafternoon thunderstorms.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
